:: Forest Shop Entrance
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "forest_shop">><<effects>>
<<specialClothesRefresh>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $enteringForestShop>>
	<<set _justEntered to true>>
	<<unset $enteringForestShop>>
<</if>>
<<if $enteringForestShopTogether>>
	<<set _enteredTogether to true>>
	<<unset $enteringForestShopTogether>>
<</if>>
<<set _shopEvent to (!$robin_in_forest_shop and !$daily.gwylan.eventShop and !Time.isBloodMoon() and ["garden", "shop"].includes(gwylanSchedule()) and C.npc.Gwylan.state is "active")>>

<<if $forest_shop_intro isnot 1>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Intro">>
<<elseif _justEntered and _shopEvent and _gwylanStatus.includes("reunion")>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>><<unset $gwylanSteal>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Reunion">>
<<elseif _justEntered and !$robin_in_forest_shop and _gwylanStatus.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Nowhere">>
	/* ToDo: Gwylan bad end - walking into the shop after escaping  */
<<elseif _justEntered and _shopEvent and $dissociation gte 1 and !$weekly.gwylanTrauma>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>><<set $weekly.gwylanTrauma to true>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Trauma">>
<<elseif _justEntered and !$robin_in_forest_shop and $gwylanSteal and !Time.isBloodMoon()>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>><<unset $gwylanSteal>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Thief">>
<<elseif _justEntered and _shopEvent and _gwylanLovePercent gte 10 and !$gwylanSeen.includes("intruder")>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Intruder">>
<<elseif _justEntered and _shopEvent and _gwylanLovePercent gte 85 and C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 120 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3 and $gwylanSeen.includesAll("partners", "hypnosis_deepest", "petplay") and !$gwylanSeen.includes("familiar_collar")>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Familiar Collar">>
<<elseif _justEntered and $whitney_familiar_seen is 1 and !["dungeon", "pillory"].includes(C.npc.Whitney.state) and C.npc.Whitney.init is 1 and $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Familiar Whitney">>
<<elseif _justEntered and !$gwylan.timer.randomOrgasm and $hypnosis_traits.devotion and ($arousal gte 10000 or $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast") and random(1, 40) is 1)>>
	<<set $gwylan.timer.randomOrgasm to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(14).timeStamp>>
	<<include "Forest Shop Mystery Orgasm">>
<<else>>
	<<if $gwylan.timer.eventShopEnd>>
		<<if Time.date.timeStamp gte $gwylan.timer.eventShopEnd>>
			<<run delete $gwylan.timer.eventShopEnd>>
			<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<set _snoopEvent to _shopEvent and (_justEntered or $gwylan?.timer?.eventShopEnd)>>
	당신은 숲 상점에 있다. 내부는 어둡고, 높은 선반들로 가득하며, 온갖 물건들이 들어있다. 대부분은 쓸모 없는 자질구레한 물건들이지만, 개중에 당신의 흥미를 끄는 것들이 있다.
	<br><br>

	<<if isPregnancyEnding()>>
		<<pregnancyPassout "forestShop">>
	<<else>>

		<<if _gwylanLovePercent gte 35 and !$gwylan.punishment and !$gwylan.taken and !$gwylan.timer.wrap and (pcAreArmsBound("any") or $feetuse is "bound")>>
			Your bindings catch on <<print either("a loose shelf", "a clothes hangar", "a low-hanging branch", "some unpleasantly sticky vines")>>. You try to pull away, and <span class="green">your bindings fall to tatters at your feet.</span>
			<<unbind>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<if !$robin_in_forest_shop and (gwylanSchedule() isnot "shop" or $daily.gwylan.noTalk)>>
			<<if Weather.precipitation === "rain">>
				빗소리의 잔잔한 음색을 제외하면, 가게는 조용하다.
			<<else>>
				가게는 조용하다.
			<</if>>
			<<if $daily.gwylan.noTalk or isGwylanAbsent() is "nobody">>
				<<if isGwylanAbsent() is "nobody">>
					아무도 없다.
				<<else>>
					그윌란은 없는 것 같다.
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("fox_plushie_gwylan")>>
					카운터 위에 놓인 커다란 여우 인형의 목에, 작은 표지판이 걸려 있다.<br>
					내용은 다음과 같다:
				<<else>>
					카운터 근처에 작은 표지판이 놓여 있다. 내용은 다음과 같다:
				<</if>>
				<<if gwylanSchedule() is "cafe">>
					'아침 식사로 외출 중. 지불은 거스름돈 없이, 딱 맞게 해 주세요!'
				<<elseif gwylanSchedule() is "garden">>
					'정원에 있음. 지불은 거스름돈 없이, 딱 맞게 해 주세요!'
				<<else>>
					'곧 돌아옵니다. 지불은 거스름돈 없이, 딱 맞게 해 주세요!'
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if $robin_in_forest_shop>>
				로빈은 코스튬들을 감탄하며 바라보느라 바쁘다.
				<br>
				<<if !$halloween_robin_costume or $halloween_robin_costume is "ghost">>
					<<socialiseicon>><<link [[로빈과 이야기한다|Robin Forest Costume Intro]]>><</link>>
				<</if>>
			<<elseif _snoopEvent and _gwylanLovePercent gte 20 and $gwylanSeen.includes("intruder", "clothes_intro") and !$gwylanSeen.includes("hat_found")>>
				<<set $gwylan.timer.eventShopEnd to new DateTime(Time.date).addHours(3).timeStamp>>
				가게는 조용하고, 당신은 그윌란을 어디에서도 찾을 수 없다. 그리고, <span class="purple">가게는 평소보다 어둡다.</span>
				<br>
				<<investigateicon>><<link [[그윌란을 찾아본다|Forest Shop Hat]]>><</link>>
			<<elseif _snoopEvent and _gwylanLovePercent gte 35 and $gwylanSeen.includes("hat_found") and !$gwylanSeen.includes("lights") and $gwylan.progress gte 3 and $gwylan.requestCount gte 2>>
				<<set $gwylan.timer.eventShopEnd to new DateTime(Time.date).addHours(2).timeStamp>>
				가게는 조용하고, 당신은 그윌란을 찾을 수 없다. <span class="purple">가게는 평소보다 어둡다.</span>
				<br>
				<<investigateicon>><<link [[그윌란을 다시 한 번 찾아본다|Forest Shop Lights]]>><</link>>
			<<elseif _snoopEvent and _gwylanLovePercent gte 50 and $gwylanSeen.includes("lights") and !$gwylanSeen.includesAny("caught", "caught_no_lewd") and $gwylanTalked.length gte 10 and $gwylan.progress gte 6 and !(["clothing"].includes($gwylan.request.event) && gwylanRequestMet())>>
				<<set $gwylan.timer.eventShopEnd to new DateTime(Time.date).addHours(2).timeStamp>>
				가게는 조용하고, 당신은 그윌란을 찾을 수 없다. <span class="purple">가게는 평소보다 어둡다.</span>
				<br>
				<<investigateicon>><<link [[Try to find the hidden room again|Forest Shop Snoop]]>><</link>>
			<<else>>
				<<if Time.isBloodMoon()>>
					<<set $gwylan.timer.bloodVisit to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(1).timeStamp>>
					그윌란은 가게 안을 돌아다니고 있다. 그는 가끔 창가에 멈춰 서서 붉은 하늘을 바라보다가, 다시 어둠 속으로 사라진다.
				<<else>>
					어둠 속 어딘가에서 그윌란이 부스럭거리는 소리가 들려온다.
				<</if>>
				<br>
				<<socialiseicon>><<link [[그윌란을 찾아본다|Gwylan Talk Shop]]>><</link>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<br>

		<<icon "clothingshop.png">><<link [[옷들을 본다|Forest Shop]]>><</link>>
		<br>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("lights")>>
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("sample")>>
				Some strips of decorated cloth hang from a line of rope.
				<br>
				<<investigateicon>><<link [[Examine them|Forest Shop Charms]]>><</link>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<<if $gwylan.timer.sample gte Time.date.timeStamp>>
					Some charms sway gently in a breeze you can't feel.
					<br>
					<<investigateicon>><<link [[Examine the charms|Forest Shop Charms]]>><</link>>
				<<else>>
					<<mysteryicon>><span class="purple">The charms have all burnt out, and are unreadable.</span>
				<</if>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>

		<<if !$robin_in_forest_shop and $gwylanSeen.includes("doggy_bed")>>
			<<if !$gwylan.timer.petBed>>
				<<bedicon "gwylanpet">><span class="purple">You can't find <<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>your pet bed<<else>>the bed Gwylan left out for you<</if>>.</span>
			<<else>>
				<<set _doggyBedText to $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1 ? "Your pet bed" : "Pet bed">>
				<<bedicon "gwylanpet">><<link [[_doggyBedText|Forest Shop Dog Bed]]>><</link>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<</if>>

		<<if $christmas_gift_robin is undefined and $christmas is 1 and C.npc.Robin.init is 1>>
			<<if isLoveInterest("Robin")>><<gifticon "love">><<else>><<gifticon "christmas">><</if>><<link [[로빈을 위한 선물을 찾아본다 (0:10)|Forest Christmas Robin]]>><<pass 10>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if isPubfameTaskAccepted("gwylan")>>
			<<if $pubfame.gwylan.snowglobe isnot 1>>
				<<icon "snowgsnowglobelobe.gif">><<link [[스노우볼을 찾아본다 (0:20)|Forest Snowglobe]]>><<pass 20>><</link>>
			<<elseif $money gte 2000 and ["shop", "garden"].includes(gwylanSchedule())>>
				<<icon "snowgsnowglobelobe.gif">><<link [[스노우볼을 산다 (£20)|Forest Snowglobe Buy]]>><<money -2000>><</link>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<</if>>

		<br>
		<<if $robin_in_forest_shop>>
			<<getouticon>><<link [[로빈과 함께 가게를 떠난다 (0:10)|Robin Forest Shop Home]]>><<pass 10>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<<else>>
			<<getouticon>><<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><<set $forest to 0>><</link>>
		<</if>>
		<br>

		<br><br>
		<<if $shopHuntMinigameTest>>
			<span class="orange">SHOP HUNT MINIGAME TESTING</span>
			<br>
			<<ind>><<link [[Forest Shop Hunt Test|Forest Shop Hunt Test]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>

	<</if>>
<</if>>

/* Entrance override for lockout or blood moon */
:: Forest Shop Locked
<<set $location to "forest_shop">><<effects>>

<<if $yearningLetter is 2 and C.npc.Gwylan.state is "scorned" and !isGwylanAbsent()>>
	You raise your hand to the door. It creaks open. You didn't hear it unlock.
	<br><br>

	It's very dark inside.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Enter|Gwylan Yearning Start]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	You try the shop's door. It won't budge, and you don't see anything resembling a keyhole. <<if Time.isBloodMoon()>>There's a faint glow coming from within.<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Knock|Forest Shop Knock]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Shop Knock
<<effects>>
<<if $daily.gwylan.locked or $forest_shop_intro isnot 1 or C.npc.Gwylan.state is "scorned" or isGwylanAbsent()>>
	You knock on the door. There's no answer.
	<br><br>

	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.state is "scorned">>
		<<link [[Apologise|Forest Shop Scorned Apologise]]>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif Time.isBloodMoon() and C.npc.Gwylan.love gte 10 and !$gwylanSteal>>
	You knock on the door.
	<<if $wraith and $wraith.hunt>>
		<<set $gwylan.timer.bloodKnock to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(1).timeStamp>>
		Something in the building shudders, and you hear multiple additional locks clicking into place. <span class="red">You feel whatever's hunting you draw closer.</span> <<set $wraith.hunt++>><<set $foresthunt++>>
		You hope Gwylan heard you, <span class="blue"><<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> might at least come looking for you if you get caught</span>.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		After a moment of silence, you hear Gwylan's voice. "Enter." <span class="blue"><<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> sounds strangely monotone.</span> You hear multiple locks click, and the door's handle twists to let you in.
		<br><br>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("bloodmoon")>>
			<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><<set $enteringForestShop to true>><</link>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Blood]]>><</link>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	/* Fallback case */
	You knock on the door. There's no answer.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Shop Scorned Apologise
<<effects>>
"Gwylan? I'm sorry," you call out.
<br><br>

There's no answer.
<br><br>

<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3 or $wolfgirl gte 6 or $cat gte 6>>
	<<link [[Scratch at the door|Forest Shop Scorned Scratch]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Shop Scorned Scratch
<<effects>>
<<set $gwylan.scratchDoor ||= 0>>
<<set $gwylan.scratchDoor++>>
You scratch at the door like a <<if $cat gte 6>>cat<<else>>dog<</if>>.
<<if $wolfgirl gte 6>>
	You even whine for good measure.
<</if>>
<br><br>

There's still no response.
<br><br>

<<link [[가게를 떠난다|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
<br>

:: Forest Shop Blood
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "forest_shop">><<effects>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bloodmoon")>><<set $gwylan.timer.bloodVisit to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(1).timeStamp>>
<<npc Gwylan 1>><<person1>>

You enter, and the door slowly closes itself behind you. <span class="red">You can't see Gwylan anywhere.</span>
<br><br>

You hear rapid footsteps from the rear of the shop. Gwylan runs into view, holding a broomstick. <<He>> looks both relieved and confused upon seeing you. "How did you get in?"
<br><br>

"You let me in?" you reply.
<br><br>

"No, I—" <<He>> pauses, looking up to the ceiling with an annoyed expression. "Of course. Apologies, I'm a bit scattered tonight." <<He>> looks back to you with concern. "You shouldn't be out on nights like tonight, especially out here in the forest. It's dangerous." <<He>> returns to the gloom.
<br><br>

<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

<!-- Events that can happen on shop entrance -->
:: Forest Shop Intro
/* included, no effects */
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
당신은 기이한 건물에 들어간다. 내부는 어둡고, 높은 선반들로 가득하며, 온갖 물건들이 들어있다.
<br><br>

<<if _enteredTogether>>
	Gwylan lets go of your hand and gestures around <<him>>.
<<else>>
부스럭거리는 소리와 쾅 하는 소리에 침묵이 깨진다. 발판 사다리를 든 칙칙한 갈색 머리카락의 소년이 가장 가까이 있는 통로 끝에서 나타난다.
<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("met")>>
	그윌란이다.
	<br><br>
	<<if $daily.gwylan.firstMet>>
		"왔구나! I wasn't expecting you so soon, I would have put some tea on otherwise,"
	<<else>>
		"왔구나!"
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<br><br>
	"손님이잖아!"
<</if>>
그가 말하며, 사다리를 떨구고는 걸어온다. 그는 그의 앞치마에 손을 닦는다.
<</if>>
"내 가게에 어서 와."
<<if $exposed gte 1>>
	<<He>> seems completely unbothered by your <<lewdness>>.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $gwylan_rescue is 1 and $gwylanRescue.failed>>
	<<gwylanRescueApology "shop" "intro">>
	<br><br>

	"I hope you find something you like," <<he>> says<<if !_enteredTogether>>, picking the ladder back up<</if>>. "But don't worry if you don't. My grand<<father>> would say the objects here hide from people they don't want to be bought by." <<He>> giggles. "I could believe it."
<<elseif !_gwylanStatus.includes("met")>>
	그는 당신과 비슷한 나이대로 보이고, 칙칙한 갈색 머리카락에 주근깨가 언뜻 보인다. "이래 봬도 보기보다는 나이가 많아," 그가 마치 당신의 머릿속을 들여다보기라도 하는 듯 말한다. "<span class="green">난 그윌란이야.</span>" 그는 양손을 앞으로 뻗어, 당신의 손을 잡은 뒤 악수를 한다. "만나서 반가워. 난-" 그윌란은 잠시 말을 멈춘다. "내 할아버지는-" 또 다시 멈춘다. "난 이것저것 자질구레한 것들을 팔아. <span class="blue">보통 다른 상점에서는 구할 수 없는 것들을 말이야.</span> 나도 여기 재고에 뭐가 있는지 모른다니까!" 그는 자랑스럽다는 듯 말한다.
	<br><br>

	"뭔가 맘에 드는 걸 찾게 되길 바랄게," 그는 다시 사다리를 집어들며 말한다. "못 찾는다고 해도 너무 걱정하진 마. 할아버지의 말을 빌리자면, 물건들도 팔리기 싫어하는 사람한테서는 숨곤 한다니까 말이야." 그가 웃음을 터트린다. "나는 그 말을 믿어."
<<else>>
	<<He>> pinches your cheek, and smiles warmly. "I hope you find something you like," <<he>> says<<if !_enteredTogether>>, picking the ladder back up<</if>>. "But don't worry if you don't. My grand<<father>> would say the objects here hide from people they don't want to be bought by." <<He>> giggles. "I could believe it."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if ["sleep"].includes(gwylanSchedule()) or Time.hour gte 22>>
	<<if _enteredTogether>>
		Gwylan checks the time. "It's rather late, but don't worry, the shop can take care of itself. Just leave exact change on the second counter on the left."
	<<else>>
	<<He>> then pokes you on the nose. "Sneaky <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>, coming in at this hour." <<He>> giggles again. "The shop can take care of itself if I'm out. Just leave exact change on the second counter on the left."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<<elseif !["shop", "garden"].includes(gwylanSchedule())>>
	그는 무언가 생각난 듯 덧붙인다. "사실, 나는 이제 막 외출하려던 참이었거든. 걱정 마, 내 가게는 알아서 돌아가니까. 왼쪽에서 두 번째 카운터에 거스름돈 없이, 대금을 정확하게 놓아주면 돼." 그러면서 그는 가느다란 진열대에서 커다란 모자를 하나 집어 들고, 앞치마를 같은 자리에 걸어둔 뒤 쏜살같이 당신 너머의 문밖으로 나간다.
	<br><br>
<</if>>
<<set $forest_shop_intro to 1>>

<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

:: Forest Shop Thief
/* included, no effects */
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<outfitChecks>>
<<if _shirtless and _bottomless>>
	<<set _startedNaked to true>>
	As you enter the forest shop, your foot meets a ?gwylanItem on the floor.
<<else>>
	As you enter the forest shop, your
	<<if _shirtless>>
		<<bottoms>> <<is _bottom>>
	<<else>>
		<<top>> <<is _top>>
