:: Forest Shop Trauma
/* included, no effects */
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<if $gwylanRescue?.failed>>
	<<gwylanRescueApology "shop">>
	<<He>> walks up to you, and <<his>> normally bright smile sullens after getting a closer look at you.
<<else>>
	As you enter the forest shop, Gwylan skips over to you. <<His>> normally bright smile sullens after getting a look at you. "Are... are you alright? You don't look well at all."
<</if>>
<<He>> reaches out to touch you.
<br><br>

Your body roils at the gesture. <span class="red">Nothing feels real. You forget where you are.</span> All you know is that you're in the forest somewhere. Are you lost? Wooden shelves carved into trees tower into an impossibly tall canopy.
Something in the shape of a person steps away from you. <<if $awarelevel gte 4>>Something terrible, with a false name and antlers growing from its shadow.<</if>>
<br><br>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>"Please... please stay away from me!" Your voice quivers.
	<<case "bratty">>"Stay the hell away from me!" You shout, but your voice betrays your fear.
	<<default>>"Please... get away." Your voice is soft but shaky.
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan takes a deep breath as <<he>> calms <<himself>>. "Alright." <<He>> sighs and walks away. With <<him>> out of sight, you gather yourself, but your mind wanders to the many assaults you've faced. You're not safe here.
This place is no better than outside. You back yourself against the door. Your eyes dart around. They lock onto Gwylan, standing by a rotting wooden table. <<He>> sets a plate of fruits down.
"Take one. It will make you feel better."
<br><br>

<<link[[Eat one|Forest Shop Trauma 2]]>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>>
<br>
<<link[[Ignore|Forest Shop Trauma 2]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<br>

:: Forest Shop Trauma 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("trauma")>>
<<if $phase is 0>>
	<<canvas-model-override "mouth" "chew">>
	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("trauma_eat")>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("trauma_eat")>>
		You walk with slow steps over to the plate. You haven't seen these types of fruits before. Carefully, you pick one up and take a small bite. You feel a pleasant warmth and your muscles relax. They seem safe to eat. <<stress -6>><<trauma -12>><<lstress>><<lltrauma>>
	<<else>>
		You walk with slow steps over to the plate. Carefully, you pick one up and take a small bite. You feel a pleasant warmth and your muscles relax. <<stress -6>><<trauma -12>><<lstress>><<lltrauma>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	You almost animalistically eat the piece of fruit. Each bite gives you a sense of safety. You forget about the outside world as you continue to eat.
	Once you finish, you notice Gwylan out of the corner of your eye. <<He>> smiles sweetly at you.
	<br><br>

	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.love gte 25>>
		Your eyes lock on <<his>> smile. <<His>> face looks so welcoming. The shop starts to twist and meld around you, only Gwylan staying in focus. <<hallucinogen 80>><<ghallucinogens>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> holds out <<his>> arms to you. You suddenly feel so cold, and <<he>> looks so warm. Your legs move on their own, but you don't feel them. If you could, you think you'd be walking even faster towards <<him>>. You collapse in <<his>> arms.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[다음 (?:??)|Forest Shop Trauma 3]]>><<canvas-model-override "clear">><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<canvas-model-override "clear">><<endevent>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	You keep away from the plate as if it were a bear trap. A sense of uneasiness grows in your stomach. You grip the handle for the door. You grip it until your fingers ache. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
	<br><br>

	You don't open it, though. You stand there until Gwylan comes back into view. <<His>> hands are folded in front of <<him>>.
	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.love gte 25>>
		<<He>> looks a little sad, but nods at you politely before returning to the gloom.
	<<else>>
		<<He>> seems unsure of what to do, but gives you one last patient smile before returning to the gloom.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Shop Trauma 3
<<effects>>
<<set _pass to random(10, 30)>>
<<pass _pass>>
When you come to, you're lying down with your head against something soft. Your head is gently stroked, and you feel warm and fuzzy. <<ltiredness>><<lltrauma>><<tiredness -6>><<trauma -24>>
<br><br>

You struggle to open your eyes. You want nothing more than to go back to sleep.
<<if $hypnosis_traits.slumber gte 1>>
	<<hypnosisText "A sweet voice whispers in your ear, and you do just that, the last dregs of tension leaving your body.">> <<tiredness -2>><<ltiredness>>
<<else>>
	A sweet voice whispers in your ear, and you do just that, the last dregs of tension leaving your body. <span class="witchbloom">It's pure bliss. You've never had sleep so restful.</span>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<link [[다음 (?:??)|Forest Shop Trauma 4]]>><<tiredness -12>><<trauma -12>><</link>><<lltiredness>><<ltrauma>>
