:: Forest Shop Trauma 5
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("trauma_love")>>
<<if $phase is 0>>
	You nod your head wordlessly. You really do feel better. You can't remember why you were so upset.
	<br><br>

	Gwylan lets you up. "Sorry I can't give you more, those fruits don't grow on tr—" <<He>> pauses. "They're not easy to grow."
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
