	<<else>>
		<<He>> steps away, but stops on the edge of the gloom. "I can't walk this road of struggles for you, no matter how laden with thorns it is. But I can sell you a pair of shoes for the journey."
		<<He>> takes the final step, leaving you alone again.
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.noTalk to true>>
	You force yourself up out of Gwylan's grasp. <<He>> makes no effort to stop you when <<he>> realises that you're not happy.

	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
