	<</switch>>
	You stop and think for a moment. You can't remember why you were so upset when you came here. Did it help?
	<br><br>

	"I wanted to ease some of your burden. Maybe I'm out of touch. I'm sorry." <<He>> bows, before retreating behind a shelf and vanishing in the gloom.
