As you move to open the forest shop's door, it's flung open from the inside. A dark, fuzzy shape barrels into you as it flees the shop, knocking you to the ground. <<gpain>><<pain 3>>
<br><br>

The shape flees, seemingly paying you no mind. Once you get your bearings, you're able to recognise that it's a <span class="lewd"><<beasttype 1>></span> fleeing deeper into forest. You brush yourself off and enter the shop.
<br><br>

<<person1>>Gwylan stands in front of you, looking worse for wear. <<His>> apron has a few fresh rips, and <<he>> pants, holding a broom in both hands as if ready to swing it at you. <<He>> lowers it right away upon realising that it's you.
<br><br>

"Sorry. Rowdy customer.
<<if $NPCList[1].monster is "monster">>
