As you walk around, it becomes apparent that the shop isn't the same as the last time you were here. None of the shelves are in the same place. You quickly notice that there doesn't seem to be any clothing in this section, despite the abundance of wooden mannequins.
<br><br>

You spend more time wandering, until you start to feel lost. You call out to the gloom. "Gwylan?" The light echo of your voice is the only answer.
<br><br>

<<link [[Keep looking (0:05)|Forest Shop Hat 2]]>><<pass 5>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
