:: Forest Shop Hat 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _tf to checkTFparts()>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	You continue looking. You're unable to recognise what's on most of the shelves, but your eyes eventually fix on something unusual.
<<else>>
	You turn around and start to retrace your steps. You make a bit of progress, but things quickly start to look unfamiliar. <<stress 6>><<gstress>>
	<br><br>

	Eventually, you spot something that sticks out from all the unidentifiable knick-knacks.
<</if>>
There's a small depression in the wall, like there's supposed to be a door there. Next to it, there's a wooden mannequin wearing a dark green witch hat with brown animal ears sewn on. The ears get darker near the tip.
<<if _tf.foxEars>>
	<span class="pink">Your own ears twitch.</span> They're certainly meant to resemble fox ears.
<</if>>
It's the same one you saw Gwylan posing a mannequin with, and perhaps the same mannequin too. Now that you have a closer look, you notice that the flowers on the hat are very much alive. There are vines hanging from the brim.
<br><br>

You reach for it, gently taking it off of the mannequin's head. <span class="red">A wooden hand caresses your arm</span>. You jump back with a start, only to back right into someone behind you. <<stress 12>><<ggstress>>
<br><br>

You quickly turn around. It's just Gwylan.
<br><br>

<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("cautious")>>
	"Looking for something in particular? Or are you just skulking around?"
<<else>>
	"Sorry, did I scare you? I heard you call out for me and came looking."
<</if>>
You look back to the mannequin. One of its hands is raised to its mouth. You can't say for sure whether it was already like that.
<br><br>

"Oh, you found my hat! I was looking all over for it!" Gwylan smiles at you, putting it on. "Even I lose track of things here. The shop must like you if it's showing you around and trying to give you my accessories."
<<He>> holds <<his>> arms behind <<his>> back. "I know the shop can be confusing. It—" <<He>> pauses. "I... have to rearrange things frequently. Sorry, I'm a bit scattered."
Gwylan leads you around, showing you how to get back to the main section of the shop, before leaving you to your business.
<br><br>

<<link [[다음|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
