:: Forest Shop Lights
<<effects>>

<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>><<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("lights")>>
You wander around the shop again, looking for Gwylan or anything of interest. Everything on the shelves seems completely mundane to you, and you pass them by without thinking about it. You can't remember a single thing you see for more than a few seconds.
<br><br>

Instead, you feel a pull towards the back of the shop. Your legs move with purpose even if your mind hasn't quite caught up yet. You feel like you know what you're looking for and exactly where it is, moving on instinct. <<awareness 2>><<gawareness>>
<br><br>

You start to see a dim green glow peeking through the shelves. You follow it, and before too long, you're in front of a depression in the wall. The same one from last time. Green light spills from the seams. There's a door here after all. The air feels warmer, your head lighter. <<ghallucinogens>><<hallucinogen 200>>
<br><br>

It takes you a moment to find the mechanism to open it. It's... just a doorknob. But you didn't see it until your hand was on it. You give it a twist, and it opens.
<br><br>

