<<effects>><<npc Gwylan 1>><<person1>>
<<set $daily.gwylan.eventShop to true>>

The room beyond isn't pitch black this time. It's a wide room full of more wooden mannequins, awash in the green glow. <<stress 6>><<gstress>>
<br><br>

The glow is coming from further in, through an open doorframe on the other side of the room. It seems to be receding as you move towards it. You carefully navigate the maze of mannequins, and can't help but take note of the poses some of them are in.
Many hold their wooden hands up to their cheeks, their heads thrown back in
<<if $trauma gte 2500>>
