Lost in thought, you nearly trip over something heavy, but steady yourself without too much noise. It's a large bag of dirt, next to a heaping stack of identical bags. On the wall behind them is a full arsenal of gardening equipment. You look up and almost jump out of your skin as you're met with a pale face. <<ggstress>><<stress 24>>
