Some time passes in silence. Gwylan cautiously breaks it with a soothing voice as to not startle the <<beasttype 1>> further. "You're awfully nosy, sneaking in here <span class="blue">again</span>. I suppose the shop showed you the way." <<He>> doesn't sound angry, but you can't quite tell.
