<<He>> notices your confused look. "<span class="blue">You've been here once already.</span> You stumbled around in my storeroom, making all sorts of noise. I thought you were an intruder or thief." <<He>> gestures to a jar of blue powder on a nearby table. "<span class="pink">I... made you forget about it.</span>"
<<He>> pauses. "I could make sure you don't remember this time either, but you're too curious. You'll just find your way in here again. Nothing to be done about it," <<he>> finishes with a smile. "You're lucky you're so interesting."
