More silence.
<<if $phase is 1 and $tendingSuccess>>
	You pause your scrubbing, looking at the <<beasttype 1>>. <<bHes 1>> covered in bites and scratches, which you can tell were from other wolves. <<bHis 1>> fur is matted and unkempt. <<bHe 1>> hasn't been cleaning <<bhimself 1>>.
