<</if>>
<br><br>

"<span class="red">This forest is sick</span>," Gwylan says, as if reading your mind. "Although, 'cursed' might be a more fitting word. Poisoned by the careless and malicious in equal parts."
<<if $phase is 1 and $tendingSuccess>>
	<<He>> squeezes out more shampoo into your hand, alongside something else. A pungent green ooze that sizzles when it touches the water, but doesn't burn.
