"This poison spreads through the vegetation, into the animals that eat it, and then into the animals that eat them. <span class="purple">It grows like an infection,</span> until it inundates everything. It makes plants grow wild, strangling the earth, the animals, and each other.
It makes beasts more aggressive, seeking out human prey when they otherwise wouldn't. I do all I can to treat them." As if on queue, the <<beasttype 1>> relaxes further. "It's an old concord. Making sure it never reaches the point of no return has been my..." <<He>> pauses. "My family's responsibility for generations."
