"I made it just for you," <<he>> says with a slight blush. <<He>> turns the heart around, revealing <span class="lewd">your name engraved on it</span>. <<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3>><<arousal 400>><<hypnosisText "<<garousal>>">><</if>>
<br><br>

"It's very special. I've... let's say, I've attuned it to you and I. It's a trick collar, of sorts. Normally, it won't do anything special, but I can... lock it." <<He>> caresses your neck.
"If you let me do so, <span class="blue">no one but me will be able to remove it.</span> It'll protect your neck, and no one will even be able to attach a leash to it. Except me, of course."
<br><br>

<<He>> walks around you, and wraps <<his>> arms around you. "<span class="green">It might just let me know if you're in danger nearby, too.</span> There's just one catch."
<br><br>

<<He>> plants a kiss on your neck. <<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3>><<hypnosisText "The tension leaves your body.">><</if>>
"It will <span class="lewd">make your trance last until it's removed.</span> You don't mind though, do you?" <<His>> voice is honey dripping into your mind.
<br><br>

"Won't you let me put it on you, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">>? It would mean the world to me."
<br><br>

