<<else>>
	You hear rapid footsteps approaching, and Gwylan emerges from the gloom. "There you are!" <<He>> walks up and hugs you. "I was starting to wonder if you had forgotten about me. What happened to you?"
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<gwylanReunion>>
<br><br>

<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("badEndReady")>>
