	<br><br>

	The floor attacks you from below, but Gwylan guides you down slowly. "Shhh... just... a little longer."
	<br><br>

	<<His>> voice fades away with the rest of the room.
	<br><br>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
