<</if>>

You awaken harshly, feeling as though you just hit the ground back-first. You gasp and thrash.
You try to, at least. <span class="red">Your limbs feel impossibly heavy.</span> You try to move your neck, but even that comes with great effort.
<br><br>

The room you're in is dark, dimly lit by candles that surround you in what you assume to be a circle. You lay on a quilted rug, encircled by a large symbol on the floor. <span class="blue">You feel clean, as if freshly washed.</span>
<br><br>

<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	"My dearest." Gwylan's voice sends a warm shiver through your body.
<<else>>
	"My dearest." Gwylan's voice startles you.
<</if>>
<<He>> sits down next to you, <<his>> face awash with worry and the slightest hint of shame. "I hope you can forgive me."
<br><br>

<<He>> leans over you and puts the tip of <<his>> finger on your forehead. "Forgive me for not keeping you safe."<br>
<<His>> finger trails down to the tip of your nose. "Forgive me for not acting sooner."<br>
Finally, <<his>> finger presses against your lips. "And forgive me for this act of selfishness."
<br><br>

<<He>> throws a leg over you to straddle you. "Your absence has torn me open. I need your touch. I need to make sure you're healed before you can face the outside world again, and only then can I, myself, heal."
<br><br>

You're stuck to the floor like a squashed insect, although you feel more like one put up in pins in a display case.
<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	<<hypnosisText "Your heart aches with guilt.">> You've made <<him>> so worried. <<stress 10>><<trauma 10>><<ggstress>><<ggtrauma>>
<<elseif $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
	<<hypnosisText "Your heart aches with a guilt you're not sure is your own.">> <<stress 4>><<trauma 4>><<gstress>><<gtrauma>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> leans down and embraces you. <<He>> couldn't hold you any closer without being under your skin.
<br><br>

<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3 or $trauma gte 9000>>
	<<link [[Ask Gwylan to take care of you|Forest Shop Taken Start 2]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 10>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 20>><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote>><<gglust>><<gggyearning>>
	<br>
<</if>>
