			Is this some revenge of yours, some spite, because I wouldn't return your feelings?" <<His>> hand lightly pets your head. <<His>> tone is unnervingly neutral. "This is larger than us, dear."
			<<npcincr Gwylan dom -50>><<lllyearning>>
			<br><br>

		<</if>>
		<<He>> doesn't seem angry, yet the hairs on the back of your neck stand on end. <<stress 6>><<gstress>>
		<br><br>

		"You've made a ruinous mistake. The scar will never go away. If you fail to reverse course, it will only become worse. It won't be fast. It will surround your heart like a serpent, constricting it. Then, it will take a single bite.
		To taste you. To measure your value as a vessel. Regardless of the outcome, it will proceed to swallow you." <<His>> eyes bore into you, and you're afraid to move. "You won't die. <span class="red">You'll wish you could, though.</span>"
		<br><br>

		<<He>> caresses your cheek with the back of <<his>> hand. "Why did you let the Elk's servants do this to you?"
	<<else>>
		"I expected this would happen sooner or later. Your scar defies our union. It strives to keep us apart, so we can't heal the forest." <<He>> gently pets your head. "I won't hold your past mistakes over you. You've already helped me much.
		I'm certain you already have regrets, else you wouldn't keep coming here." <<He>> doesn't seem angry, yet the hairs on the back of your neck stand on end. <<stress 6>><<gstress>>
		<br><br>

		<<His>> smile is sad. "The scar will never go away. If you slip further, it will grow in turn. It won't be fast. It will surround your heart like a serpent, constricting it. Then, it will take a single bite.
		To taste you. To measure your value as a vessel. Regardless of the outcome, it will proceed to swallow you." <<He>> looks like a parent telling their child that their pet just passed away. "You won't die. <span class="red">You'll wish you could, though.</span>"
		<br><br>

		<<He>> caresses your cheek with the back of <<his>> hand. "Sate my curiosity, if you could, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>. Why did you let the Elk's servants do this to you?"
	<</if>>
<</if>>
