	Just before you make it out, the entire store seems to <span class="red">creak</span>. You look down at your feet, searching for loose floorboards, but find nothing. You quickly exit the shop.
<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("steal_again")>>
	Your eyes dart around, looking for Gwylan. The way out seems clear. You hastily make for the exit with your stolen clothes.
	<br><br>

	Just before you make it out, the entire store seems to <span class="red">creak</span>. It almost sounds <span class="red">angry</span>. You quickly exit the shop.
<<else>>
	You make a break for the forest shop's exit with your stolen clothes. <span class="red">The floor creaks with each step you take.</span> Several intruding objects poke out from every shelf, wardrobe and piece of esoteric furniture you pass by, which you swear weren't there when you entered. Despite your best efforts, you can't avoid them all. Your clothes are repeatedly caught.

	<<set $stripintegrity to 120>>
	<<switch random(1,4)>>
