You're blinded as the doors open, revealing the forest. You're harshly spit out on the grass in front of the shop. You hear a door slam shut behind you, <span class="red">and a lock click into place</span>.
<br><br>

You struggle to stand, your arms bound behind you by something. You look down. <span class="lewd">You're covered in nothing but gift wrappings.</span> The shop rhythmically creaks from behind you, as if laughing.
<br><br>

<<specialClothesUnlock "set" "wrap">>

