:: Forest Shop Sex Toys Intro
<<effects>><<npc Gwylan>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("sexToys")>>

You approach the unfamiliar cabinet and peek inside it. <span class="lewd">It's filled with unusual devices.</span> Some look like <<= $awareness lte 200 ? "silicone sculptures" : "dildos">> fashioned after fantastical creatures. <<= $awareness lte 200 ? "Some of them have" : "A few of them appear to be buttplugs with">> tails attached. Others are clearly antique: a leather saddle with a phallus affixed to it; a hand-cranked mechanism with an oscillating end; a percussion massager with a thick cord that appears to screw into a lightbulb socket. A fragile sheet of paper tacked to the back of the cabinet claims that its "vibratory massage" cures insomnia, intestinal and digestive disorders, rheumatism, and gout.
<br><br>

"How did you find this?" a voice from behind you says.
<br><br>

You jump. "Sorry, I didn't mean to pry," you say, unable to mask your guilt. "I'd just never seen this before, and..."
<br><br>

"It's fine," Gwylan says. <<Hes>> blushing a little. "That's not what I meant. I'm just... wondering why the shop decided to show you this now? I haven't looked at these in years."
<br><br>

<<He>> wipes some dust off one of the dildos and examines it.
<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("strapOnGifted")>>
