<<else>>
	"This is a collection of vintage or novelty items I've picked up over the years. I'll admit, I don't tend to use them on my own. There's plenty of other ways to alleviate any masturbatory urges. But sharing a toy with a fluid-bonded partner... well. It's rather intimate." <<He>> gives you a fond smile. "I suppose it's telling me that it might be time to break them out again. The non-antique ones, anyway. I doubt either of us could get off using some of the more archaic devices here."
<</if>>
